               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18420404-name-1398" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18420404-name-1398" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18420404-name-1398" type="surname" value="SAUSSEY"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18420404-name-1398" type="given" value="JAMES"></interp>JAMES SAUSSEY</persName>
                  </hi>. I am a cabinet-maker, and live in Beersland-street, Kingsland-road. I was at Greenwich fair on Monday the 28th of March, and lost my handkerchief there—this is it.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Cross-examined by</hi> 
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">MR. PAYNE</hi>. <hi rend="italic">Q.</hi> It is a very poor one, is it not? <hi rend="italic">A.</hi> Yes—I know the handkerchief by its being full of holes.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18420404-name-1399" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18420404-name-1399" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18420404-name-1399" type="surname" value="JACKSON"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18420404-name-1399" type="given" value="CHARLES"></interp>CHARLES JACKSON</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-constable A</hi> 126.) I was on duty at Green-which fair—I saw Hunt take the handkerchief from the prosecutor's pocket, and give it to Grabbit—I immediately took them both into custody—I had been watching them previously—they were both together.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Cross-examined. Q.</hi> You are quite sure you saw it? <hi rend="italic">A.</hi> Quite sure—I was quite close to them—I was in plain clothes.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Hunt. Q.</hi> Did you hold up the handkerchief when you took me, and ask if the bystanders had lost one? <hi rend="italic">A.</hi> Yes—I did so to let the prose<lb></lb>cutor know he might come to the station.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18420404-name-1400" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18420404-name-1400" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18420404-name-1400" type="surname" value="MUMFORD"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18420404-name-1400" type="given" value="JOHN PASSMORE"></interp>JOHN PASSMORE MUMFORD</persName>
                  </hi>. I am a policeman. I was at Greenwich fair—I saw Hunt lay hold of the prosecutor's pocket, take the handkerchief from it, and hand it to Grabbit—I took Hunt, and took him to the station.</p>
               <p>(Grabbit received a good character.)</p>
